---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Cart from '../components/Cart.astro';
---

<Base
  title="About Us"
  description="Jagannath Publications — preserving and sharing the sacred literature of Srila Gour Govinda Swami Maharaja."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="pt-28 pb-20">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 text-center mb-12 sm:mb-16">
      <p class="font-display text-xs tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-brand-500 font-semibold mb-3">
        About Us
      </p>
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)] leading-tight mb-5">
        Seva through the Printed Word
      </h1>
      <p class="font-display text-lg sm:text-xl text-[var(--text-muted)] leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Jagannath Publications is a devotional imprint dedicated to one purpose — placing
        the words of Srila Gour Govinda Swami Maharaja into the hands of every sincere
        seeker.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Ornament divider -->
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8">
      <div class="ornament">
        <svg width="42" height="22" viewBox="0 0 42 22" fill="none" class="text-[var(--accent)]" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M21 20 C21 20 8 20 4 14 C9 14 13 12 15 8 C16 11 18 13 21 14 C24 13 26 11 27 8 C29 12 33 14 38 14 C34 20 21 20 21 20 Z" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.45"/>
          <path d="M21 14 C21 14 17 11 18 5 C20 7 21 10 21 14 Z M21 14 C21 14 25 11 24 5 C22 7 21 10 21 14 Z" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.55"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Mission block -->
    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 py-10 sm:py-14 space-y-8">
      <article class="prose-block">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
          For over three decades, Srila Gour Govinda Swami delivered the purest message of
          the <em>Srimad-Bhagavatam</em> in temples, huts, and living rooms across the
          world. Thousands of hours of his lectures, bhajans, and intimate darshans were
          recorded — but much of it still rests unheard. Our work is to transcribe, edit,
          translate, print, and distribute these teachings exactly as he spoke them.
        </p>
      </article>

      <!-- Values grid -->
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 sm:gap-5 my-10">
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6.042A8.967 8.967 0 006 3.75c-1.052 0-2.062.18-3 .512v14.25A8.987 8.987 0 016 18c2.305 0 4.408.867 6 2.292m0-14.25a8.966 8.966 0 016-2.292c1.052 0 2.062.18 3 .512v14.25A8.987 8.987 0 0018 18a8.967 8.967 0 00-6 2.292m0-14.25v14.25"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Fidelity</h3>
          <p>Every word is cross-checked against the original recordings. Nothing is polished away.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 008.716-6.747M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 01-8.716-6.747M12 21c2.485 0 4.5-4.03 4.5-9S14.485 3 12 3m0 18c-2.485 0-4.5-4.03-4.5-9S9.515 3 12 3m0 0a8.997 8.997 0 017.843 4.582M12 3a8.997 8.997 0 00-7.843 4.582m15.686 0A11.953 11.953 0 0112 10.5c-2.998 0-5.74-1.1-7.843-2.918m15.686 0A8.959 8.959 0 0121 12c0 .778-.099 1.533-.284 2.253m0 0A17.919 17.919 0 0112 16.5c-3.162 0-6.133-.815-8.716-2.247m0 0A9.015 9.015 0 013 12c0-1.605.42-3.113 1.157-4.418"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Accessibility</h3>
          <p>Four languages in print today — more on the way. Affordable pricing for every reader.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 8.25c0-2.485-2.099-4.5-4.688-4.5-1.935 0-3.597 1.126-4.312 2.733-.715-1.607-2.377-2.733-4.313-2.733C5.1 3.75 3 5.765 3 8.25c0 7.22 9 12 9 12s9-4.78 9-12z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Devotion</h3>
          <p>Not a business. Every rupee returns to printing the next title and supporting the temple.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <article class="prose-block">
        <h2>Two Imprints, One Family</h2>
        <p>
          Our titles are published under two devotional imprints founded in service of Srila
          Gour Govinda Swami's mission:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Gopal Jiu Publications</strong> — established at the ISKCON Bhubaneswar
            temple to publish the monthly <em>Sri Krsna-kathamrta</em> magazine and allied
            booklets in English, Hindi, and Bengali.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Tattva Vichar Publications</strong> — dedicated to longer works,
            translated volumes, and the multi-volume <em>Sri Radha</em> and
            <em>Guru-tattva</em> series.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="prose-block">
        <h2>Over 80 Titles. One Message.</h2>
        <p>
          From slim introductory booklets to the landmark <em>Sri Radha — Ocean of
          Krsna-prema</em>, our catalog spans every stage of the devotional journey. You will
          find works on the glories of the Holy Name, the science of the guru, the pastimes
          of Lord Jagannath, Vedic family life, and the innermost mood of Sri Caitanya
          Mahaprabhu.
        </p>
      </article>

      <!-- Stats row -->
      <div class="stats-row">
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-num">80+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Titles in Print</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-num">4</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Languages</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-num">3,000+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Hours of Audio</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-num">30+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Years of Service</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="text-center pt-6">
        <a
          href="/books/"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-7 py-3 bg-brand-500 hover:bg-brand-600 text-white rounded-full font-display text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase transition shadow-md"
        >
          Browse the Library
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
  <Cart />
</Base>

<style>
  .prose-block h2 {
    font-family: 'Gatwick', Georgia, serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1rem;
  }
  .prose-block h2::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.5rem;
    bottom: 0.5rem;
    width: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--brand), var(--accent));
    border-radius: 2px;
  }
  .prose-block p,
  .prose-block ul {
    font-family: 'Gatwick', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }
  .prose-block ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding-left: 0;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }
  .prose-block ul li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .prose-block ul li::before {
    content: '◆';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--brand);
    opacity: 0.6;
  }
  .prose-block p em,
  .prose-block li em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .value-card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.25s ease;
  }
  .value-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--brand);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.1);
  }
  .value-icon {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.1), rgba(201, 169, 110, 0.1));
    color: var(--brand);
    margin-bottom: 0.875rem;
  }
  .value-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Gatwick', Georgia, serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.375rem;
  }
  .value-card p {
    font-family: 'Gatwick', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .stats-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 2rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }
  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .stats-row {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    }
  }
  .stat {
    text-align: center;
  }
  .stat-num {
    font-family: 'Gatwick', Georgia, serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--brand);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .stat-label {
    font-family: 'Gatwick', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }
</style>
